            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息全線向下   H按息率跌破2厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14949739&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息全線向下。與樓按相關的一個月拆息(HIBOR)跌至0.66613厘，連跌5日，再創近3年低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_FB_2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250429_PP_HK-PROPERTY_BP_FB_2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以現時一般新造H按計劃「H+1.3厘」計算，今日H按實際按息已跌至1.966厘，跌穿2厘水平，也創3年低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">以平均按揭額400萬元，25年計，封頂息每月供款20025元，H按息每月供款16896元，較封頂息月供少3129元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜息0.02833厘，跌0.744基點 ; 1期報0.23292厘，跌0.756基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">3個月拆息報1.70976厘，跌0.869基點 ; 6個月拆息報2.5667厘，跌4.047基點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14949739-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e5%90%91%e4%b8%8b-h%e6%8c%89%e6%81%af%e7%8e%87%e8%b7%8c%e7%a0%b42%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-23 08:35:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價下跌　市場關注OPEC+增產",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價下跌，市場關注石油輸出國組織及其盟友（OPEC+）可能進一步增產。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油報每桶61.2美元，跌37美仙，跌幅0.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶64.44美元，跌47美仙，跌幅0.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14951441-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%b8%8b%e8%b7%8c%e3%80%80%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%97%9c%e6%b3%a8opec%e5%a2%9e%e7%94%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-23 08:35:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股道指升229點後平收　美債息回順",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數走勢反覆，收市個別發展，道瓊斯工業平均指數蒸發全部升幅，大型科技股造好納斯達克指數升。美國國債孳息率回順。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_25097747709006.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_25097747709006.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數低開96點後，跌幅擴大至最多146點，低見41714點，尾段最多倒升229點，高見42090點；但最終蒸發全數升幅，收市報41859點，跌1點，連跌3交易日。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數一度升1%，收市報18925點，升53點，升幅約0.3%。一度回升0.57%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數報5842點，跌2點。曾反彈1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Tesla升近2%，Nvidia和亞馬遜升近1%。Alphabet一度創3個月高位，收市升約1.4%。但蘋果偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場近期憂慮美國債務情況推高美債息，令股市受壓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"><strong> 30年長債息率曾升5.78基點</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在美國眾議院通過總統特朗普的稅收和支出議案後，債息回落紓緩股市壓力。10年期債息一度高見4.629厘，創逾3個月高位，其後回落至4.5厘水平。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國30年期債息一度上揚5.78個基點，至5.1501厘，創2023年10月以來高位，其後回軟至5厘水平。1年期債息反覆曾跌6.2個基點，至4.535厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14951428-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87229%e9%bb%9e%e5%be%8c%e5%b9%b3%e6%94%b6%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%9b%9e%e9%a0%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-23 08:35:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
